lves the requested library, runs Native Image with `Preserve` and `TrackDynamicAccess`, and prints a JSON summary suitable for issue comments.\\n\\n### Generating Metadata\\n\\nGenerates metadata for a single library coordinate. If `agentAllowedPackages` is provided, a new user-code-filter.json will be created or updated from those packages or from package roots derived from the resolved library JAR.\\n\\n- `coordinates`: group:artifact:version (single coordinate only)\\n- `agentAllowedPackages`: comma-separated package list, `fromJar`, or `-` for none\\n\\nExamples:\\n   ```console\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=org.example.app,com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777410282293}}\n340:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0f5d175e182b10ad0169f120e980d8819784d139068efea416\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp8SDq6zsC3VDhSWmdQg-rxAdgzkt3Bz66_jtsKtEYeu3eDZRO_yffoG8esiBsJvlGBQFOAeDIXT2432N9R5aoMh37OkQLTCb_e0RCGS5F-Nz77rYf8tjnW5xlV2QpOdYyZTzG4R7lw1dq2MlRdb-zzHIzcNXYCPAYRZDxZIvJQHcPukVKs2PF81v6TfnNBm3X_xknU8UAZpUEu7wlqYLF6tS4nN-jrCJlr89AIkL689ehfhKc4NLTz2nc3ek3m6X3DX-4h6EjpkVWfchAW8d71FFQOjJwgyvYGTm8CYYJ719O7RKb7iEzCn7y_PNL6Yu8m_Cjs5zV1Ef5yZczD06x20o5Nfx4NkWQTs_htX4bXoQtkbhGfhjKMBJWSNkVn8Vm6sBBo4pLscDrDtevtSFCLRqwvmqFpROiKTKDtbd6VV5qlpnYxe-o_zXFZd27T9UnJBhnKQpEFPGnUiJTEnCYg3JA62ss5voDWclYLiKDH7CzAcQ0lDSS1lSF31T8l8sBHRy7NGexLeK63kpBmXThf-f906DC1tN87tH_kBnx5uyZYSmMpkojK6VLFD336iabTTdw_YXodG1LyJVrLHvTrYoZ5lSO7KxVOBJC1mVguB7JTLauj43e6ELFELC_iwIZsgVIhkcl35bCLDfLr7VaXnauSUEDy